<note n="0267010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0267010">唯＝惟【明】＊</note>
<note n="0267011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0267011">汝＝法【宮】</note>
<note n="0267012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0267012">在＝存【宋】【宮】，＋（存）【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0268001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0268001">菀＝苑【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0268002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0268002">滋＝資【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0268003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0268003">之＝足【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0268004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0268004">空法＝空性【宮】</note>
<note n="0268005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0268005">卷第六終【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0268006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0268006">〔大方等大集經日藏分〕－【三】</note>
<note n="0268007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0268007">卷第七首【三】缺此卷【宮】</note>
<note n="0269001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0269001">加＝跏【宋】【明】</note>
<note n="0269002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0269002">陀＝那【明】</note>
<note n="0269003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0269003">（世）＋界【三】</note>
<note n="0269004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0269004">別＝莂【元】【明】＊</note>
<note n="0270001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0270001">楊＝揚【三】</note>
<note n="0270002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0270002">不分卷，〔大方…譯〕三十二字－【三】</note>
</p>
